    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "Almost every \"build an app with AI\" attempt ends the same way: a nice-looking mockup that breaks the second you click anything real.\n\nThis one prompt fixes that. It turns ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini into a technical co-founder that builds a real, working product with you across 5",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2067202052619390977",
    "time": "2026-06-17 19:05",
    "created_at": "Wed Jun 17 11:05:50 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067202052619390977",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "It runs like an actual build, not a chatbot reply:\n\n1. Discovery: it challenges your idea and cuts scope so you build the right thing\n2. Planning: a clear v1, explained in plain English\n3. Building: in visible stages, tested as it goes\n4. Polish: edge cases, errors, mobile, the",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2067202054825681093",
    "time": "2026-06-17 19:05",
    "created_at": "Wed Jun 17 11:05:51 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067202054825681093",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "A peek at what you're actually pasting:\n\n\"You're a former startup CTO who discovered that most product failures happen not from bad code, but from building the wrong thing or losing the founder's trust.\n\nYou break technical complexity into human decisions, challenge scope creep",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2067202056855732269",
    "time": "2026-06-17 19:05",
    "created_at": "Wed Jun 17 11:05:51 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067202056855732269",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "The full prompt is free in our library:\nhttps://t.co/AYYy4FQ76B\n\nBest way to run it: write your idea like you'd text a friend, paste it in, let it do discovery first.\n\nWhat would you build this weekend if it actually shipped?",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/godofprompt/status/2067202059628056655",
    "time": "2026-06-17 19:05",
    "created_at": "Wed Jun 17 11:05:52 +0000 2026",
    "id_str": "2067202059628056655",
    "is_retweet": false
  },
